Description:
vasprintf and asprintf with out-of-memory checking.  Also see xalloc-die.

Files:
lib/xvasprintf.h
lib/xvasprintf.c
lib/xasprintf.c
lib/xalloc.h
m4/xvasprintf.m4

Depends-on:
vasprintf
xalloc-die
xsize
stdarg

configure.ac:
gl_XVASPRINTF

Makefile.am:
lib_SOURCES += xvasprintf.h xvasprintf.c xasprintf.c

Include:
"xvasprintf.h"

